<pb ed="X" id="X26.0568.0932a" n="0932a"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a01"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a02"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a03"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a01"/>
<ab type='juan' subtype='open'>般若波羅蜜多心經</ab><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a04"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a05"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a06"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a03"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>觀自在菩薩。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>阿難說。我教有觀自在者。變化從心<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a07"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a04"/>達觀自得也。觀聽圓明。智慧無礙。觀有不住有。觀<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a08"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a05"/>空不住空。心不能動。境不能隨。動隨不亂其真。得<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a09"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a06"/>大自在圓通也。菩薩即菩提薩埵之省文。菩提曰<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a10"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a07"/>覺。薩埵曰有情。謂能覺一切有情。自覺以覺眾生<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a11"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a08"/>也。曰菩薩。曰大士。皆尊稱佛號之名也。觀自在菩<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a12"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a09"/>薩。即觀世音大士也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a13"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a10"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>行深般若波羅蜜多時。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>行深者。謂清淨因地之法<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a14"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a11"/>行已深也。功行最深。具大智慧。造到彼岸之時。多<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a15"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a12"/>者定也。時者時候也。菩薩妙覺圓明。超出世間。具<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a16"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a13"/>足三昧慧定之時也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a17"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a14"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>照見五蘊皆空。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>照者。本心智慧。妙覺明照也。見者。<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a18"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a15"/>本心智慧。明圓真見也。五蘊者。色受想行識之五<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a19"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a16"/>陰也。空即本心性體。寔相之真空也。照見蘊空。則<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a20"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a17"/>本心妙明。而性體洞見也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a21"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959a18"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>度一切苦厄。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>謂解脫一切執著。生死煩惱之苦厄。<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a22"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b01"/>成就一切圓通也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932a23"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b02"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>舍利子。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>即舍利弗母名舍利。因母立名。乃佛之弟<lb
 ed="X" n="0932a24"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b03"/>子舍利弗。于佛弟子之中。智慧第一。而不能如觀<pb ed="X" id="X26.0568.0932b" n="0932b"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0932b01"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b04"/>世音菩薩。究竟得證圓通。而成正覺者。盖因滯于<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b02"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b05"/>智慧也。滯于智慧。有我相我見。空相空見。佛故覺<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b03"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b06"/>觀自在菩薩之行深般若真空無相之法。以證菩<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b04"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b07"/>提彼岸。得為圓明普照之標榜。呼舍利子而告之<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b05"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b08"/>欲其不滯于我相我見。空相空見。而究竟于人空<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b06"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b09"/>法空空之境界。以證無上道也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932b07"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b10"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>色不異空。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>色乃夢幻泡影。故不異于空也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932b08"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b11"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>空不異色。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>空乃一真顯露。故不異于色也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932b09"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b12"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>色即是空。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>色有形相。凡所有相。皆是虗妄。終有壞<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b10"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b13"/>期。故色即是空也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932b11"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b14"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>空即是色。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>空性虗無。無形無聲者也。道以虗無之<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b12"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b15"/>體。視之不見。聽之不聞。能生有色有聲之天地萬<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b13"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b16"/>物。故空即是色。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932b14"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b17"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>受想行識。亦復如是。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>因色而有六根之領受。六根<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b15"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0959b18"/>領受于心。而生思量擬度之想。懸相六塵。而生運<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b16"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a01"/>用施為之行。行動遷流。而生分辨精粗美惡之識。<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b17"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a02"/>色受想行識五者相因也。色有壞時。而受想行識<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b18"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a03"/>終歸虗妄。亦復如是。色即是空也。能了悟色即是<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b19"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a04"/>空。逢色不受。則無受想行識諸雜念。一心清淨。空<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b20"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a05"/>若太虗。以無相而生真空之寔相。亦復如是。空即<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b21"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a06"/>是色也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932b22"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a07"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>舍利子。是諸法空相。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>佛呼舍利子之名。進一層以<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b23"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a08"/>告之也。意謂。不但五蘊皆空。一切修證菩提之法。<lb
 ed="X" n="0932b24"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a09"/>莫不皆空。</ab></div><pb ed="X" id="X26.0568.0932c" n="0932c"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c01"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a10"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>不生不滅。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>真性累劫不壞。故不生不滅。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c02"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a11"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>不垢不淨。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>真性本來無染。故不垢不淨。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c03"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a12"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>不增不減。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>真性不著一物。自然恰好。不增不減也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c04"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a13"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是故空中無色。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是故承上起下之詞。是故真空之<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c05"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a14"/>中。本無我相。何色之有。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c06"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a15"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無受想行識。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>既無我相。自無我見。一切聲色。何能<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c07"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a16"/>入我真空妙明之心。自無受想行識矣。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c08"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a17"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無眼耳鼻舌身意。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>既無我相。則六根亦非我有。無<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c09"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960a18"/>耳鼻舌身意矣。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c10"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b01"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無色聲香味觸法。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>六根既無則六塵無。安頓之所。<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c11"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b02"/>自無色聲香味觸法矣。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c12"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b03"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無眼界。乃至無意識界。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>亦通目之所見。為眼界。心<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c13"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b04"/>之所之。為意識界。眼為六根之先鋒。意為六識之<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c14"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b05"/>主帥。而六根六塵。無識不顯。無眼界乃至無意識<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c15"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b06"/>界。則六根六塵六識之十八界。皆無界矣。今眼界<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c16"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b07"/>既空。則萬緣悉泯。而意識胥忘。將見由定而靜由<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c17"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b08"/>靜而慧。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c18"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b09"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無無明。亦無無明盡。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無無明亦無無明盡。無無者。<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c19"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b10"/>無昏昧之慮也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c20"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b11"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>乃至無老死。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>由久而固。由固而貞。無老死者。常存<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c21"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b12"/>不壞也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0932c22"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b13"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>亦無老死盡。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無明至老死。乃佛所說三世十二因<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c23"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b14"/>緣也。一曰無明。謂過去世。妄識迷性也。二曰行。謂<lb
 ed="X" n="0932c24"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b15"/>過去世。一切結業。隨無明妄識流轉也。三曰識。謂<pb ed="X" id="X26.0568.0933a" n="0933a"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0933a01"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b16"/>現在世。托胎識靈種子也。四曰名色。謂現在世。識<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a02"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b17"/>靈在胎。心但有名。而色身已有質也。五曰六入。謂<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a03"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0960b18"/>現在世。識靈在胎。已成六根之體。已具六入之用<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a04"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a01"/>也。六曰觸。謂現在世。色身出胎之後。六根但有所<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a05"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a02"/>觸。尚未了知六塵之涉入也。七曰受。謂現在世。色<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a06"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a03"/>身日漸長大。已能納受六塵諸境。尚于貪淫等。心<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a07"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a04"/>未起也。八曰愛。謂現在世。色身日益長成。貪淫等<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a08"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a05"/>心已開。而生種種愛欲。尚未寔愛欲之境也。九曰<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a09"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a06"/>取。謂現在世。色身強壯。愛欲日盛。而馳求恣取色<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a10"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a07"/>聲香味觸等。以寔愛欲之境也。十曰有。謂現在色<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a11"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a08"/>身。因馳求恣取。六根積集欲界色界無色界三界<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a12"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a09"/>之因。成就欲有色有無色有三界之業果也。十一<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a13"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a10"/>曰生。謂因果不亡。識靈又隨業流轉。受生衰老。又<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a14"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a11"/>壞而死也。因無明緣行。因行緣識。因識緣名色。因<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a15"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a12"/>名色緣六入。因六入緣觸。因觸緣受。因受緣愛。因<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a16"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a13"/>愛緣取。因取緣有。因有緣生。因生緣老死。十二因<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a17"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a14"/>緣生滅無常。有起有盡。盡而復起。起而復盡。循環<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a18"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a15"/>三世。生滅輪轉。若觀此十二因緣。皆明無為妄識<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a19"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a16"/>流轉。忽然覺悟十八界皆空。則本妙明心。如如不<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a20"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a17"/>動。無有生滅之妄識。則無無明明矣。既無無明明。<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a21"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961a18"/>無起無盡。亦無無明盡矣。乃至者。色無行亦無行<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a22"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b01"/>盡。無識亦無識盡。無名色亦無名色盡。無六入亦<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a23"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b02"/>無六入盡。無所觸亦無觸盡。無受亦無受盡。無愛<lb
 ed="X" n="0933a24"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b03"/>亦無愛盡。無取亦無取盡。無有亦無有盡。無生亦<pb ed="X" id="X26.0568.0933b" n="0933b"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0933b01"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b04"/>無生盡。無老死亦無老死盡。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933b02"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b05"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無苦集。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>苦謂生死煩惱諸苦。集謂積聚。人生在世。<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b03"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b06"/>心為形役。形為世勞。積聚五蘊中之根塵處界。十<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b04"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b07"/>二因緣。生死煩惱種種苦因。今既無五蘊根塵處<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b05"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b08"/>界。十二因緣。則無苦因之積聚也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933b06"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b09"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>滅道。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>滅謂集滅。道謂真常不息之道。五蘊中一切<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b07"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b10"/>苦因。一一皆生滅無常。今生滅既滅。寂滅現前。而<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b08"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b11"/>當體妙明。寂靜之真性。洞徹圓通。以入真常不息<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b09"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b12"/>之大道。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933b10"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b13"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無智亦無得。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>謂既無苦集滅道。則已入佛慧。明了<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b11"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b14"/>無礙之智。已得菩提之果。然雖入佛智。乃本心般<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b12"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b15"/>若真空之本智。般若無智。無所不知。無漏之智。如<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b13"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b16"/>無智也。雖得菩提之果。亦是本心現量。即心即佛。<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b14"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b17"/>不假外求。亦無所得也。若知有智。乃曲心推測之<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b15"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0961b18"/>知見。非真空無漏之本智也。若云有所得。即有所<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b16"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a01"/>失。亦有漏本心。具足本智。故云無智亦無得也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933b17"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a02"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>以無所得故。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>此承上起下之詞。謂一心之本智本<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b18"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a03"/>法。本自具足。無心外之法可得。若有一法可得。即<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b19"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a04"/>有一分識心結習未盡。識心結習若盡。則萬法本<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b20"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a05"/>具一心。一心本具萬法。一心與萬法不二。萬法與<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b21"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a06"/>本心本一。復何有所得哉。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933b22"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a07"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>菩提薩埵。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>菩提薩埵。梵語菩提薩埵。華言菩薩。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933b23"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a08"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>依般若波羅蜜多故。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>以般若波羅蜜多。為修行之<lb
 ed="X" n="0933b24"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a09"/>法。守其六根。絕其六塵。依因也。謂依般若之本智<pb ed="X" id="X26.0568.0933c" n="0933c"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0933c01"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a10"/>本慧。自悟自修。以登彼岸之故。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933c02"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a11"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>心無罣礙。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>罣者懸擊。礙者窒塞。依一心之本智。不<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c03"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a12"/>依緣起之業識。不住客塵之妄法。則心是空心。法<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c04"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a13"/>皆空法。所謂不依一法。而心常住。已得大自在矣。<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c05"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a14"/>復何罣礙之有乎。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933c06"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a15"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無罣礙故。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>故心無牽罣滯礙。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933c07"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a16"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>無有恐怖。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>恐怖如地陷風飄。火燒水溺。及殺害惡<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c08"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a17"/>死。五蘊非有。常清常靜。不動不搖。一切如如。復何<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c09"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962a18"/>驚恐怖畏之有乎。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933c10"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b01"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>遠離顛倒夢想。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>顛倒謂六塵惑亂。妄想成業。生滅<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c11"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b02"/>施復。虗妄輪轉。種種顛倒也。夢想謂惑于見思客<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c12"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b03"/>塵。而迷夢妄想也。若既無恐怖。則障垢已盡。本性<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c13"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b04"/>不復更迷。虗妄不復更生。復何三界感業。而輪轉<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c14"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b05"/>顛倒。復何見思惑亂。而迷夢妄想乎。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933c15"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b06"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>究竟涅槃。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>涅云不生。槃云不滅。謂本心本無罣礙。<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c16"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b07"/>本無恐怖。顛倒夢想。一切種種。皆緣起於無始無<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c17"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b08"/>明。虗妄業識耳。今既依當身一心本智。外息諸緣。<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c18"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b09"/>內心無喘。心如墻壁。外不放入。內不放出。真常真<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c19"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b10"/>樂。真我真靜。究竟直到不生不滅涅槃之大道。至<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c20"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b11"/>于不生不死而後已。不但菩薩為然也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933c21"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b12"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>三世諸佛。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>即三世諸佛。欲得無上菩提。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933c22"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b13"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>依般若波羅蜜多故。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>亦無有不依般若波羅蜜多。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0933c23"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b14"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>阿耨多羅云無上也。三<lb
 ed="X" n="0933c24"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b15"/>藐云正等。三菩提云正覺。絕諸對待。無有而上之<pb ed="X" id="X26.0568.0934a" n="0934a"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a01"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b16"/>者。故名阿耨多羅無上也。本心本智。各自具足。故<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a02"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b17"/>名三藐正等也。本心般若智慧。本不為塵勞所蔽。<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a03"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0962b18"/>故名三菩提正覺也。謂行深般若之本心本智。到<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a04"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a01"/>波羅密之彼岸。而證菩提之果。不但觀自在菩薩<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a05"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a02"/>而然。即過去現在未來三世諸佛。莫不依般若波<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a06"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a03"/>羅密多故。得無上正等正覺之大道也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a07"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a04"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>故知般若波羅蜜多。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是知般若波羅蜜多。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a08"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a05"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是大神呪。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是變化不測之密語。統妙萬法。不可思<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a09"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a06"/>議。之謂神。呪者。秘密心印也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a10"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a07"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是大明呪。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是神光普照之密語。普照一切。而無所<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a11"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a08"/>不遍。之謂明。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a12"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a09"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是無上呪。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是至極無加之密語。最極一切。而無上<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a13"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a10"/>可上。之謂無上。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a14"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a11"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是無等等呪。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>是獨絕無倫之密語。一切平等。無等<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a15"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a12"/>可等。之謂等等。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a16"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a13"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>能除一切苦。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>謂度脫一切生死煩惱苦厄也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a17"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a14"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>真實不虗。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>佛無妄語。如來所說。是真語寔語如語<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a18"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a15"/>不誑語不異語也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a19"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a16"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>故說般若波羅蜜多呪。</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>更有密呪。如其誦之。可以<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a20"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a17"/>生智慧。可以到彼岸矣。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a21"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963a18"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='prose'>即說呪曰。</ab>
<ab type='dharani'>揭諦揭諦</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>揭出妙諦。以度人也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a22"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b01"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='dharani'>波羅揭諦</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>重言之。自度度他也。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934a23"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b02"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='dharani'>波羅僧揭諦</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>欲到彼岸。必須賴此妙諦也。僧眾也。<lb
 ed="X" n="0934a24"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b03"/>薩婆訶疾速也。謂疾速成就一切眾生也。</ab></div><pb ed="X" id="X26.0568.0934b" n="0934b"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0934b01"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b04"/><div type='orig' level='2'><ab type='dharani'>菩提薩婆訶</ab></div><div type='commentary' level='2'><ab type='prose'>大凡一切呪語。乃諸佛總之密呪。雖<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b02"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b05"/>修行之徑路。而徑路不外于此心。人能空其五蘊。<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b03"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b06"/>則主翁常定。而客感自清。豈有不得無上菩提者<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b04"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b07"/>哉。微妙秘密心印。不可以意識思議。而妄下注解。<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b05"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b08"/>不但不能下注解。亦不必下注解。惟當沉沉靜靜。<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b06"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b09"/>無思無慮。一心持念。無記無數。即呪是心。即心是<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b07"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b10"/>呪。不復以知見立知見。如此持念一心。至于知見<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b08"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b11"/>無見。則群魔于此以降。真如此以住。罣礙恐怖。于<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b09"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b12"/>此而解脫。顛倒夢想。于此而遠離。本智本慧。于此<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b10"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b13"/>而開發。無明煩惱。于此而盡泯。即無明是大智。即<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b11"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b14"/>煩惱是菩提。即菩提是五蘊。即五蘊是法身。即法<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b12"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b15"/>身是諸法。即諸法是空相。即空相是當身一心。即<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b13"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b16"/>當身一心。是如來藏也。般若波羅蜜多心經心呪<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b14"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b17"/>之功德。寧可思議哉。</ab></div><lb
 ed="X" n="0934b15"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0963b18"/><ab type='verse'>
願以此功德　　普及於一切　　我等與眾生　　<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b16"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a01"/>皆共信奉行　　
</ab><lb
 ed="X" n="0934b17"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a02"/><ab type='prose'>南無祇園會上佛菩薩。<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b18"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a03"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0934b19"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a04"/></ab><div type='w' level='2'><head>金剛神呪</head><lb
 ed="X" n="0934b20"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a05"/><ab type='dharani'>唵齒臨。唵部臨。諸佛現身。遮羅神。護羅神。念佛千遍。<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b21"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a06"/>鬼離身。身離床。病離身。一切邪魔化為塵。也有草神<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b22"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a07"/>陀羅尼。也有鬼神陀羅尼。諸惡鬼神謗不得。奉請十<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b23"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a08"/>地金剛滅。南無動地金剛。南無出山走水金剛。南無<lb
 ed="X" n="0934b24"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a09"/>天降四海金剛。南無父母金剛。有人念得金剛呪。免<pb ed="X" id="X26.0568.0934c" n="0934c"/><lb
 ed="X" n="0934c01"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a10"/>了身邊災。天光地光。晝夜神光。神佛自至。邪魔消亡。<lb
 ed="X" n="0934c02"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a11"/>若有善男子善女人。每日靜心念一卷。如轉金剛經<lb
 ed="X" n="0934c03"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a12"/>三十萬卷。又得神明加護。眾神提携。智慧知天地。若<lb
 ed="X" n="0934c04"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a13"/>有人書寫一本。與人流傳。功德高如須彌山。深如大<lb
 ed="X" n="0934c05"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a14"/>海。無量功德。永世不踏地獄門。處處難聽達摩耶。娑<lb
 ed="X" n="0934c06"/><lb
 ed="R092" n="0964a15"/>婆訶</ab></div></div>
</body></text></TEI>